# CodeViz

Local-first code graph and project Q&A tool.

## npm CLI

```bash
npm install -g codeviz
codeviz setup
```

Non-interactive setup:

```bash
codeviz setup --yes --provider openai --api-key sk-... --default-port 39127
```

After setup, no extra `export` is required if you saved the key in setup:

```bash
codeviz analyze <project>
codeviz open <project>
codeviz ask <project> "How is login implemented?"
codeviz compare <project> "login" --from-version v1 --to-version HEAD
```
